.@RepMeuser responds to an elderly viewer's concerns on Pres. Trump & the coronavirus:

"Those who are suffering the most symptoms...are over the age of 70... I do think the President is trying to be calming...and when we have better solutions we will be communicating that" https://t.co/cXmFwk9EKa

full_text: Tomorrow morning at 8AM, I will join Washington Journal on @cspan to discuss the federal response to the coronavirus. Be sure to tune in.
